{
  "stem": "150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The best I could come up with, really, would be I'm a Jew because I know that I am a Jew and because other people assume that I am a Jew.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I am not religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I find it very difficult to believe in a personal god, a god who is concerned with an individual, specifically.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I find it difficult to observe the rituals because I believe that if God is indeed all knowing, that he knows what is in everybody's heart.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there is no need for me to stay there-- stand there and tell God how wonderful I think he is and how much I love him because he knows whether I mean it or not.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This is a personal thing, and I, I can go through the paces.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I don't really believe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "At the same time, I'm extremely envious of those who do because it is so much more comforting and so much better for a life to be so absolutely sure that there is an afterlife and that there is a power, and that you are fulfilling his commandments when you do the things that you're supposed to be doing.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's comforting, and I wish I could.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I can't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A number of things happened to me personally over the last couple of months which lead me, or might lead me, to believe, you know, that there is a god, and that there is a god that takes an interest.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I'd rather not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But but even the fact that I managed to survive might indicate to someone of a different mental bent that I was saved in order to do what I have done, that there was a divine purpose in it.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
